v0.1.2 (22 Feb 2013)
	Added "exit" event.

v0.1.1 (20 Feb 2013)
	Added exit code to "shutdown()".
	Fixed exit code when a worker dies due to an error in the start or shutdown
		listeners or a callback with error in the shutdown, now returns 1.
	Some bugfixes.
	
v0.1.0 (19 Feb 2013)
	Added "dom()".
	Removed domain properties from the emitted error objects.
	Workers now accept a timeout before killing them.
	Some bugfixes.

v0.0.4 (16 Feb 2013)
	Uncaught exceptions were killing the application.
	Exit timeout now kills correctly the master/worker (keep-alive was preventing
		to kill the worker)

v0.0.3 (16 Feb 2013)
	Prevent from calling "shutdown()" more than one time.
	Better support for workers.

v0.0.2 (15 Feb 2013)
	Added "timeout()".

v0.0.1 (14 Feb 2013)
	First commit.